by javiereguiluz at 2016-01-13T20:55:47Z

Tests are fixed. Thanks to our test suite, we can assure that these are the only relevant HTML/CSS changes that could break a heavily customized backend:

| Before              | After
| ------------------- | -------------
| #header-menu        | .sidebar-menu
| form#content-search | .action-search form
| #content-actions    | .global-actions

It's a matter of changing 3 selectors, so I'm happy with the BC breaks.

Besides, the name of the main CSS and JS files have changed:

```
/admin/_css/admin.css -> /admin/_css/easyadmin.css
/js/admin.js          -> /js/easyadmin.js
```

